THE BROWN FILE

Name: Kwame Brown

Age: 29

Specs: 6-foot-11, 270 pounds

NBA team/position: Charlotte Bobcats/center

2010-11 stats: 7.9 ppg., 6.8 rpg., started 50 games, played in 66 games.

Pro career: 10 seasons; Washington Wizards (No. 1 pick overall in 2001 NBA draft), Los Angeles Lakers, Memphis Grizzlies, Detroit Pistons, Charlotte Bobcats.
